<law type="statute"><section id="id595"><amendatorysection chaptername="State Administrative Departments" statutenumber="81-3518" amended="yes"><bookinfo>Revised Statutes Supplement, 2025</bookinfo><statuteno>81-3518</statuteno><catchline>Responsible charge, defined.</catchline><para>Responsible charge means personal responsibility for the technical and financial aspects of geologic work through:</para><para>(1) Personal action;</para><para>(2) Management in an organization; or</para><para>(3) Direct supervision.</para></amendatorysection></section><source><para>Laws 1998, LB 1161, &#167; 66; </para><para>Laws 2025, LB38, &#167; 15. </para><effectivedate>September 3, 2025</effectivedate></source></law>
